import React from 'react';
import { Form, Input, Row, Col, Checkbox } from 'antd';

const AlamatTab = ({ form, type }) => {
  return (
    <Row gutter={16}>
      <Col span={24}>
        <Form.Item name="non_aktif" valuePropName="checked">
          <Checkbox>Non-Aktif</Checkbox>
        </Form.Item>
      </Col>

      {type === 'edit' && (
        <Col span={12}>
          <Form.Item label="No Pemasok" name="no_pemasok">
            <Input disabled />
          </Form.Item>
        </Col>
      )}

      <Col span={type === 'edit' ? 12 : 24}>
        <Form.Item
          label="Nama"
          name="nama"
          rules={[{ required: true, message: 'Nama wajib diisi' }]}
        >
          <Input />
        </Form.Item>
      </Col>

      <Col span={24}>
        <Form.Item label="Alamat" name="alamat">
          <Input.TextArea rows={3} />
        </Form.Item>
      </Col>

      <Col span={8}>
        <Form.Item label="Kota" name="kota">
          <Input />
        </Form.Item>
      </Col>

      <Col span={8}>
        <Form.Item label="Provinsi" name="provinsi">
          <Input />
        </Form.Item>
      </Col>

      <Col span={8}>
        <Form.Item label="Kode Pos" name="kode_pos">
          <Input />
        </Form.Item>
      </Col>

      <Col span={12}>
        <Form.Item label="Negara" name="negara">
          <Input />
        </Form.Item>
      </Col>

      <Col span={12}>
        <Form.Item
          label="Telepon"
          name="telepon"
          rules={[
            { pattern: /^[0-9+\- ]+$/, message: 'Format telepon tidak valid' },
          ]}
        >
          <Input />
        </Form.Item>
      </Col>

      <Col span={12}>
        <Form.Item
          label="Faksimili"
          name="faksimili"
          rules={[
            {
              pattern: /^[0-9+\- ]+$/,
              message: 'Format faksimili tidak valid',
            },
          ]}
        >
          <Input />
        </Form.Item>
      </Col>

      <Col span={12}>
        <Form.Item label="Kontak" name="kontak">
          <Input />
        </Form.Item>
      </Col>

      <Col span={12}>
        <Form.Item
          label="E-mail"
          name="email"
          rules={[{ type: 'email', message: 'Format email tidak valid' }]}
        >
          <Input />
        </Form.Item>
      </Col>

      <Col span={12}>
        <Form.Item
          label="Halaman Web"
          name="halaman_web"
          rules={[{ type: 'url', message: 'Format URL tidak valid' }]}
        >
          <Input addonBefore="https://" />
        </Form.Item>
      </Col>
    </Row>
  );
};

export default AlamatTab;
